{
  "id": "adv_card_mhk_51_01",
  "title": "miho 1話 mihoのやってみたいこと",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣の企画は、ドーナツ屋の一日店長……\n遙子のは……この間のキャンプね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei’s project was to be a donut shop manager for a day……\nAnd Haruko’s was… the camping one from a while ago……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.7666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 4.7666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3666.6666666,
          "startTime": 8.4333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "それ、『ミラクル☆アイドルバースデー！』の記事\nですよね。mihoさんにもオファーが来たんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's the \"Miracle☆Idol Birthday!\" article‚\nright? Did you get an offer too‚ miho-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "遙子の企画にゲストで出演した時\n「ぜひ」って話をいただいたのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I appeared as a guest on Haruko’s project‚\nthey told me‚ “Please join”.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "ただの社交辞令かと思ったら\n本当にオファーをもらえるなんてね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought it was just a diplomatic remark‚\nbut I didn’t expect to actually get an offer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったんですね。あ、もしmihoさんも\n誰かゲストを呼ぶなら、私、参加してみたいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. Oh‚ if you're inviting a guest too‚ miho-san‚\nI’d like to participate.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.6679658846,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "貴方を……？　随分貪欲なのね\nBIG4なら、仕事には困っていないでしょうに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You…? You’re quite greedy‚ aren’t you?\nYou’re part of BIG4. It’s not like you lack work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "困っているというか、その……\n単純にmihoさんと一度、お仕事がしてみたくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s not that I’m lacking work‚ but… um…\nI just really want to work with you‚ miho-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "経験豊富な先輩ですし、機会があれば\nもっと近くで学ばせてもらいたいと思ってます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re such an experienced senior‚ and if I get the chance‚\nI’d love to learn from you up close.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "持ち上げるのは勝手だけど\n貴方に学ばせてあげる義理はないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You can flatter me all you want‚\nbut I’m not obligated to teach you anything.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "ただ……義理はないけれど、サニーピースがゲストに\n来るなら注目度も上がるでしょうし、悪くはないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However… while I have no obligation‚ if Sunny Peace is coming as a guest‚\nthe show will have more attention. It wouldn’t be a bad idea.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "いいわ。もちろんアドバイスなんてする気はないし\nするとしても苦言を呈するくらいだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fine. However‚ I have no intention of giving you advice‚\nand if I did‚ it would only be harsh criticism…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "それでも良ければ、先方に伝えておいてあげる\nまぁ、スケジュール次第でしょうけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But if you’re okay with that‚ I’ll let them know.\nWell‚ it depends on our schedules though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます！\n{user}さんに伝えて調整してもらいます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you!\nI’ll let {user}-san know and get it sorted.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "―― A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.0666665395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.2
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "それでは早速、企画について、二人でアイデアを出し\n合いましょう。って、mihoさん、どうかしました？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ let’s start brainstorming ideas together.\nWhat’s the matter‚ Miho-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.5333332062
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "……なんでこんな会議がセッティングされてるのかしら\n怜にはただ、「ゲストに呼ぶ」って言っただけよね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Why has this meeting been set up?\nI only told you I was going to invite you as a guest…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.1333332062
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "す、すみません、何度確認しても、「まだ決めてない」\nっておっしゃるので、二人で決めた方が早いかなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I'm sorry. I asked you multiple times‚ but you kept saying‚ “I haven’t decided yet‚”\nSo I thought it would be faster to decide together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.8529871143,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.8999998729
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "私も早めに準備を始めたいですし、なんだか、その\n楽しみ過ぎて、最近あまり眠れなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I also want to start preparing early‚ and I'm so excited\nthat I haven’t been able to sleep well lately…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.2999998729
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……私の企画は遠足でも文化祭でもないのよ\nそこそこの仕事だからって、一喜一憂して。まだ子供ね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sigh… This isn’t a field trip or a school festival.\nTo be getting all worked up over a simple job… You’re still a child.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 146.8666665395
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "仕事の大きさは関係ありません。私にとっては\nmihoさんと共演出来る、いい機会なんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The scale of the work doesn't matter. To me‚\nthis is a great opportunity to work with you‚ miho-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 155.0333332062
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、はしゃいでるのは否定出来ませんけど……\nあ！　それより何か企画でやりたいことはありますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I can’t deny that I’m excited though……\nAh! Anyway‚ is there anything you want to do for the program?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 164.4999998729
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "mihoさんの好きなこととか、プライベートなこと\nってあまり聞いたことがないので、気になります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve never really heard about what you like‚\nor anything personal about you‚ So I'm curious.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 172.2666665395
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "企画になるようなことはしてないわ\nアイドルやライブの研究なんて、つまらないでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t do anything interesting that would make a good segment for the project.\nI just study idols and their performances‚ but that would be boring.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 178.3666665395
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、企画で『やってみたいこと』ならあるわね\nfranとkanaを正座させて、膝に石畳をのせたり",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However‚ there is something I’d like to “try” for the project.\nLike making Fran and Kana kneel and putting paving stones on their lap.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 186.8666665395
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 191.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
