      "text": "ただ、家庭的なイメージはⅢXのイメージと遠いから\n企画で見せるなら、本格的な料理の方がいいかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But a domestic image doesn’t really suit IIIX‚\nSo if I were to do a cooking segment‚ I think it would have to be something more professional.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 231.4666717529,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
