      "text": "いいですね！　企画名は、『ビストロmiho』とか？\nせっかくなら、mihoさんに料理を習ってみたいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That sounds great! Could we call it “Bistro miho”?\nIf we’re doing this‚ I’d like to learn how to cook from you‚ miho-san.",
